channel.title: Project Insanity HELP
channel.description:
How do I make a teleport so you don't need runes and how do I make a teleport, teleport to a certain coord.
How do I add training onto a NPC because when I try to train it won't give me any XP.
How do I make my dragon claw spec take up 50% spec because when I use it, it takes no energy away. Can somebody help on atleast one? I will be happy and will rep++ when I can!

item.title: Project Insanity HELP
item.dc:creator: @Ironclad722 Ironclad722
item.description:
@Ironclad722 wrote:

i can tell you, that if you want a teleport with NO runes, heres an example:

case 51013: case 6004: c.getPA().startTeleport(2809, 3435, 0, "modern"); c.sM("You have been teleported to the skilling area."); break;

this is a teleport for Catherby. You can edit the coords to your liking. I’m pretty sure that someone already posted a tut about PI stuff
